---
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="mt-24 border-t border-white/5">
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-5xl gap-8 px-4 py-12 md:grid-cols-3">
    <div>
      <div class="mb-2 flex items-center gap-2 text-base font-bold text-ink">
        <span class="grid h-6 w-6 place-items-center rounded-md bg-gradient-to-br from-neon-cyan via-brand-500 to-neon-violet text-[12px] font-black text-void">链</span>
        {SITE_TITLE}
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted">
        聚焦区块链与加密货币的学习笔记。跨链、DeFi、稳定币与钱包安全，用大白话讲清楚，
        希望对同样在探索 Web3 的你有帮助。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-ink">热门主题</div>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-muted">
        <li><a class="transition-colors hover:text-neon-cyan" href="/tags/跨链">跨链 / 跨链桥</a></li>
        <li><a class="transition-colors hover:text-neon-cyan" href="/tags/DeFi">DeFi</a></li>
        <li><a class="transition-colors hover:text-neon-cyan" href="/tags/稳定币">稳定币</a></li>
        <li><a class="transition-colors hover:text-neon-cyan" href="/tags/钱包安全">钱包安全</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold text-ink">站点</div>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-muted">
        <li><a class="transition-colors hover:text-neon-cyan" href="/blog">全部文章</a></li>
        <li><a class="transition-colors hover:text-neon-cyan" href="/about">关于本站</a></li>
        <li><a class="transition-colors hover:text-neon-cyan" href="/rss.xml">RSS 订阅</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="border-t border-white/5 py-6 text-center text-xs text-muted">
    © {year} {SITE_TITLE} · 内容仅为科普与学习参考，不构成任何投资建议
  </div>
</footer>
